André Sogliuzzo https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Andr%C3%A9_Sogliuzzo 0 André Sogliuzzo (born August 10, 1966) is an American actor, comedian and voice actor. He is well known for his work in films and television series. He voices Camo and Voodood in the Skylanders franchise and provides additional voices for several video games.
